For a comparison of pt with ag, see file build-ag .
(Don't use pt because it sometimes crashes.)

# Get version number from
# https://github.com/monochromegane/the_platinum_searcher/releases/
# 2.1.6 was released 7/7/2018, is most recent as of 7/2018.
VERSION=2.1.6

mkdir -p ~/bin/install
cd ~/bin/install
\rm -rf pt_linux_amd64.tar.gz pt_linux_amd64
wget https://github.com/monochromegane/the_platinum_searcher/releases/download/v$VERSION/pt_linux_amd64.tar.gz
tar xzf pt_linux_amd64.tar.gz
mkdir -p $HOME/bin/`uname`-`uname -m`
cd $HOME/bin/`uname`-`uname -m`
\ln -sf ../install/pt_linux_amd64/pt pt


Useful command-line arguments to pt:
  -U  don't pay attention to VCS ignore files such as .gitignore
